subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Angie Bjorklund scored 23 points, including seven 3-pointers, and No. 4 Tennessee made a team- and tournament-record 16 3-pointers to beat No. 16 Kentucky, 90-65, on Sunday.
